The hotel is in a good location (for good restaurants nearby head towards Rue Mouffetard) and the hotel is very clean with lovely furniture and tastefully decorated.	We slept with a fan running and windows open (into an interior well between buildings.)	We are an older couple and went to Paris to get engaged - it was all perfect and the hotel's ambience added to the experience.	The decor was either right up to date & retro or still left over from the 70s.